        <p>Plate ID: <%= product.plateId || 'N/A' %> (AM)</p>
        <p>Cutting Notes: <%= product.dieCuttingNotes || 'N/A' %> (AN)</p>
    </div>

    <br>

    <div>
        <h2>Winding Section:</h2>

        <p>Finished QTY: <% product.labelQty || 'N/A' %> (AA)</p>
